description:
Dotard's Escape is a funny, quirky story of a prisoner attempting to escape from the most absurd, dangerous and splatter of mazes.

Guide the character through intricate mazes full of dangerous traps and collect the maps you'll find along the path: they are the only hope to not loose your way and find the exit! If you think you can surviveÃ¢â‚¬Â¦

Do you think you have an idea for a personal and extravagant new trap? Let us know on our Facebook support page!
The funniest and lethal traps will be implemented into the game and made available in the next update! And your name will be in the game!

FEATURES

-Endless hours of gameplay with different mazes; 
-extensive customization about size and complexity; 
-large quantities of traps, one more lethal than the others;
-gore option: if you're faint of heart don't turn it on! 
-you can choose between free virtual joypad and stationary digital keyboard;
-free and frequent updates, including new traps proposed by the players!

What's New:

- New key option: find it to open the door and escape;
- New gore option: if you're faint of heart don't turn it on!
- New hazard: watch out for the oil spill, it won't be easy to avoid the traps while sliding;
- New traps: the maze is even more dangerous!
- New algorithm for creating mazes: now you can choose alternative paths
- Improved environments and some more graphic enhancements
- Compatibility with xperia commands and exit function

